- **Itemset:** a collection of one or more items, e.g. {Milk, Bread}
- **k-itemset:** an itemset containing k items
- **Frequent itemset:** an itemset whose support ≥ minimum support threshold
- **Association rule:** an implication $X \Rightarrow Y$, e.g. {Milk, Diaper} $\Rightarrow$ {Beer}
